  * contrib/rdd_ads/rddads.h
    + Added support for DBINFO(DBI_DB_VERSION), DBINFO(DBI_RDD_VERSION),
      and ADSVERSION([<nType>]) (but only for nType == 0 and nType == 3
      and without date and time information for nType == 3).

